{"tid":1263803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"採訪王全璋日本記者遭便衣公安按在地上","createTime":"2019-06-28T11:08:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T11:09:54.000Z","uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2543950cc861f8e28598535db9e4d3a0eea560b3","tid":1263803,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:08:07.000Z","msg":"李文足到監獄等候見王全璋 日本記者採訪遭便衣驅趕<br />\n<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1465532_1_20190628152235.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1465532_1_20190628152235.jpg&h=dee4144e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465532-20190628.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465532-20190628.htm&d=UUYXYMm1a91OOf%2FewiyebXfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=83517f09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1465532-20190628.htm&h=060cc29c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1465532-20190628.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n維權律師王全璋的妻兒和姊姊，到達山東臨沂監獄準備與王全璋會面。<br />\n<br />\n他的妻子李文足、兒子王廣微和姊姊王全秀等人，下午1時50分左右到達臨沂監獄，709家屬之一的王琑嶺也有陪同前往。據了解，會面時間大約半小時，監獄方面會先查證家屬的身分，家屬需提供身分證和結婚證書等，完成查證後，再等安排會見。<br />\n<br />\n有日本記者拍攝李文足等人的等候情況時，被幾名便衣男子驅趕，期間更有3至4人將手持攝影機的日本記者按在地上，並將記者趕離監獄門外，在監獄周圍都停泊了便衣和國保的車輛。"},{"pid":"9c3c6ea9c001c79e942037eaf28c284ea31ccdba","tid":1263803,"uid":126099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:09:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b472c8b8e1671759c028aca0165775f7119a74a","tid":1263803,"uid":126099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T11:09:54.000Z","msg":"比安倍入第一球，拎細既黎出氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}